Well, yes, I invested some time (early Kunark) in camping idols of the thorned and made enough cash to trade for a fungi.  That is the only expensive gear you need.  With just a fungi, a snare whip, and smart mob selection you can solo 45-60 reasonably well.  Truncheons of Doom are great, but I didn't use mine very much while soloing.  The reasoning being, if it was a mob I needed to use the ToD on, it was too hard to yield fast xp, even if it was a more or less guaranteed kill.<br>
<br>
Fungi (30-80k depending on your server... iksar bp is a substitue for poorer warriors), bandaids (cheap or free if you have bandaid dagger), snare whip (1k), good two hander (dime a dozen, whatever you can afford).  Get those and you are set to begin.<br>
<br>
