 <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=458241">My Sanford &amp; Son Starter Set</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mightioverlord>MightiOverlord</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/25/03 3:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ~</span><hr size=1> Warriors can solo, but the downtime is well.......boring. Takes alot of time but its good for people that cant usually get a group, or cant get one in time before they have to log due to RL stuff. i pretty much solo myself from 40-52 in some certain areas like Sol-B etc. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.angelfire.com/alt/eqtaywar/loy.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=409955">My Rusted Itemz</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
